author: Cheyenne Roundtree For Dailymail.Com
title: Man injured in car wreck pops question in hospital | Daily Mail Online
text: Man, 24, who was injured in freak ATV wreck as he was planning proposal a week before the accident finally pops question from hospital bed Brandon Trimborn, 24, was injured in an ATV accident in New Mexico in January His proposal to girlfriend Trista Wirth, 20, was just days before the accident The couple had been dating for around six months before the engagement Trimborn decided to pop the question from his hospital bed on January 18 He now is receiving care at a spinal injury rehab center in Denver, Colorado Published: 23:22 GMT, 21 February 2017 | Updated: 23:30 GMT, 21 February 2017 66 shares
